data.description: |REDUCED PRICE|Welcome to your new home in the lovely community of Millstone Cottages, conveniently located just minutes from downtown Chattanooga as well as the shopping district in Hixson! This wonderful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home was built in 2020 and beautifully finished with several upgrades, including hardwood floors throughout the home as well as a screen porch off the back of the home. Entering the front door, you'll find a beautiful foyer with an exposed brick wall. Just off the hallway, you'll find a half bath before coming to the open floorplan living room/  dining room/ kitchen. The beautiful white kitchen features an upgraded gas range and a large corner pantry for additional storage. Just off the kitchen you'll find a mudroom entrance off the 2 car garage. Off the back of the home you'll find the wonderful screen porch & flat back yard. The upstairs includes a landing area that can serve as a flex space to meet your needs - office space, den, playroom, you name it! The master bedroom features a large walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom. Rounding out the upstairs, you'll find 2 additional bedrooms, a second full bathroom and the laundry room conveniently located among the bedrooms.
